@ohhshiny I'm an old school businessman. Our white paper is a biz plan. Not building hype for a quick mint, or following anyone's pre-built template. Seems obvious to me that this needs to be done, but I understand the temptations that creators have to capitalize on the bull market frenzy.

Not sub-tweeting anyone in particular, but one thing I am definitely not going to have in this project is excess hype with inorganic growth prior to mint, slip up on execution, and get stuck with a community of 20k+ disappointed people.  Slow and steady wins the race.
